    schema1:description "Karen Bradley was Secretary of State for Northern Ireland from 8 January 2018 to 24 July 2019. She was Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport from July 2016 to January 2018. She was elected Conservative MP for Staffordshire Moorlands in May 2010."@en ;
